name: Suspicious Fruit Tandem Turnovers
desc: Pastries baked with berries. The soggy mouthfeel makes them taste as if they've been left out in the rain, and the sticky, undercooked dough clings stubbornly to the teeth... It's like something out of a nightmare.

value.text: Restores 30% of Max HP and an additional 600 HP to the selected character.
